# Local dev cruft that should NEVER end up in the image build context.
# Keeping this small speeds up `docker build` and prevents leaking secrets.

**/.venv
**/venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.py[cod]
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov

# Env files — image reads config via env vars at runtime, not baked in.
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# VCS + editor
.git
.gitignore
.idea
.vscode
**/.DS_Store

# Docs / infra we don't need inside the image
infra/
README.md
Makefile

# Local uploads / data
**/uploads
**/data
**/tmp
**/logs
